content:
To restore deleted or altered dashboards or change wizard settings, reconfigure an existing app.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
Manage CRM Analytics Templated Apps and Edit CRM Analytics Dataflows.

Reconfiguring your app gets rid of dashboard customizations. Save copies of your dataflow definition file or dashboards before proceeding. Navigate to CRM Analytics Studio and open the app.
Click the Reconfigure app link below the app name. If you see Upgrade instead of Reconfigure, upgrade the app version first.
Review the screen that warns you reconfiguring overwrites app customizations. Check the box and click Continue if comfortable with overwriting customizations.
Complete the app creation process described in Create and Share an App from a CRM Analytics Template.
Confirm your desire to reconfigure the app by clicking OK.

If you delete your app, CRM Analytics doesn't retain previous settings, requiring a new creation process. Keep the app until recreated before deleting it.
title: Reconfiguring CRM Analytics Apps
